      "writtenOn": "2026-04-13T19:23:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\"modbus\" is not a type.  That device might have multiple interfaces, and certainly doesn\u0027t share all these properties in common.  A PanasonicBJBPM102A0001PMM has a known baud rate (or set of baud rates).  It shouldn\u0027t be reading from a common type with all those properties.  We should only allow the properties that differs FOR THAT DEVICE.",
      "parentUuid": "f7cb8aef_47625be9",
      "revId": "e5bdf248b1acfda6f3ed93e2c3732a0a151c68dd",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
